      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "We should frame this as a \"security configuration oversight\" rather than a \"data breach.\" This subtle shift implies a technical misstep that was immediately corrected, rather than a catastrophic failure of human diligence. We can emphasize that the exposure window was minimal and that the affected data was non-sensitive, focusing on the swiftness of our remediation efforts. This narrative positions the company as proactive and technically sophisticated, not negligent.",
